# Mastering Nuxt with Cursor

This is a comprehensive Nuxt 4 learning project focused on mastering modern Vue.js development with Cursor AI assistance.

## Core Technologies
- **Framework**: Nuxt 4 with Vue 3 Composition API
- **UI Library**: NuxtUI v4 with Tailwind CSS v4
- **Language**: TypeScript-first approach
- **Package Manager**: pnpm
- **Code Quality**: ESLint (@antfu/eslint-config) + Prettier
- **Git Hooks**: Husky + lint-staged

## Development Philosophy
- **TypeScript-first**: All code should be written in TypeScript
- **Composition API**: Use Vue 3 Composition API exclusively
- **Component-driven**: Build reusable, composable components
- **Performance-focused**: Optimize for Core Web Vitals
- **Accessibility**: Ensure components are accessible by default
